_header: Lord how I shall me complain
_description: A burlesque love song — eight 8-line stanzas with refrain, ‘When I sleep I may not wake’

OxfBal354.First Lines:
Lord how shall I me complaynVnto myn own lady
                    dere…
OxfBal354.Last Lines:
…By this ensample ye may seThat whan I slepe I can not
                    wakffinis
